data.description: Step inside this spacious 2 bedroom plus den, 2.5 bath villa with extended lanai overlooking a beautiful lake in Marina Bay. This stunning property offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and natural beauty. You'll love the quartz counters in the kitchen with subway tile backsplash, plenty of cabinet storage, large island with filtered water faucet, and stainless steel appliances. The open-concept living space seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining family and friends. The master suite is a sanctuary with its en-suite bathroom and large walk-in closet. In the bath, you’ll find dual vanities, tile flooring and a glass enclosed shower. The guest bedroom provides an ensuite bath and walk-in closet. There’s a generously-sized den, ideal for a home office or an additional bedroom with powder bath just outside. Beyond the triple sliding glass doors, the private screened-in lanai offers serene lake vistas. This villa is not only a great place for relaxing, but Marina Bay offers a variety of recreational activities and amenities. Whether you prefer to lounge by the community pool or swim laps, play a game of tennis, pickle ball, basketball, or billiards, there's something for everyone. Your dream home awaits!
